data.value: The Beli Iskar Ecopath is located in the village of the same name. It is best to make the transition during the warm months from June to October. The trail of the trail is closed and winds along the upper course of the Beli Iskar River. Eight large and five smaller bridges cross the river. The landscapes alternate with valleys with narrow gorges, riparian relief, interesting rock formations and coniferous forests.
